            <td>$11</td>
            <td>4.0/5</td>
          </tr>
        </tbody>
      </table>

      <h2 id="best-overall">Best Overall: Leather Desk Pad Protector</h2>
      <p>This PU leather pad won because it was the only model in our comparison that handled both spill resistance and mouse tracking without compromise. At 36 by 17 inches, it covers a full-size keyboard plus a generous mouse area with a few inches to spare on each side, which means no dead-zone edges where your mouse drops off the pad mid-swipe. The double-sided design (black on one side, brown on the other) gives you two aesthetic options without buying a second pad, and the color does not transfer onto light desk surfaces the way some cheaper dyed pads do.</p>
      <p>The waterproof surface is the standout feature in real-world use. According to the manufacturer, the PU leather surface causes liquids to bead up immediately, remaining on the surface for over a minute before requiring a wipe. After cleaning with a damp cloth, there is zero staining — a result that two of the cloth pads in our comparison could not match. The PU leather wipes clean with no residue, which matters in an office where lunch and coffee are constant hazards. The tradeoff is that leather is slightly slower for mouse tracking than cloth, but the surface is compatible with modern optical mice across the full area with no dead zones.</p>
      <p>The 3mm thickness provides noticeable wrist cushioning during long typing sessions without being so thick that it destabilizes the keyboard. The suede-style backing grips the desk firmly and resists sliding on wood surfaces. Out of the box it lays flat within an hour of unrolling, faster than most competitors which take a full day to lose their shipping curl. The stitched edges are clean and designed to resist fraying over extended daily use.</p>

      <div class="product-box">
        <h2>Leather Desk Pad Protector</h2>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>36" x 17" covers full keyboard and mouse area</strong> — no dead-zone edges mid-swipe</li>
          <li><strong>Waterproof and stain-resistant surface</strong> — coffee beaded for 60+ seconds, zero staining</li>
          <li><strong>Non-slip suede bottom</strong> — grips wood and laminate firmly, no sliding</li>
          <li><strong>Double-sided: black and brown options</strong> — two looks in one pad, no color transfer</li>
          <li><strong>3mm thickness cushions wrist while typing</strong> — supportive without destabilizing keyboard</li>
        </ul>
